/
COMMENT ON COLUMN STAGE_AWARD_LEVEL_IMPORT.IMPORT_FILE_ID IS 'Identifies the import file that contains this import record.  Foreign key to the IMPORT_FILE table.'
/
COMMENT ON COLUMN STAGE_AWARD_LEVEL_IMPORT.ACTION_TYPE IS 'Indicates how to process this import record.'
/
